Author: Jalil Shojazade <jlshoja@gmail.com>
Date:   Sun Jul 12 20:53:51 2026 +0330

    Warn when compare_scans woo CSV is newer than the scan
    
    compare_scans (auto mode) diffs a fresh scan against the *previous*
    WooCommerce state. If the latest woocommerce_import CSV is newer than or
    equal to the scan, it was likely generated from that same scan, so the
    diff collapses to ~no changes — a silent footgun for a manual tool.
    
    Surface both timestamps and, in a TTY, require confirmation before
    proceeding; in non-interactive runs just log and continue. Auto mode
    only — manual mode passes explicit paths and is untouched.
    
    Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>

